.SH NAME
Notification.badge \- Notification: badge property
.SH SYNOPSIS
\f[B]Secure context\f[R]: This feature is available only in secure
contexts (HTTPS).
This feature is available in Web Workers.
.PP
The \f[B]\f[CB]badge\f[B]\f[R] read\-only property of the
\f[CR]Notification\f[R] interface returns a string containing the URL of
an image to represent the notification when there is not enough space to
display the notification itself such as for example, the Android
Notification Bar.
On Android devices, the badge should accommodate devices up to 4x
resolution, about 96 by 96 px, and the image will be automatically
masked.
.SH VALUE
A string containing a URL.
